        </a>
      </div><p>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Bastian García Pérez</strong><br />
        <br />
        I'm a selft-taught 2+ years experience software developer who started his
        profesional career after studying Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma
        degree in Madrid, Spain. Before that I spent my childhood time trying to
        develop websites on my own as a hobbie, and after completing my studies as
        a Biologist I decided to focus completely on reinventing myself as a developer.
        Since that I have focused my efforts and learning in Java technologies, specially
        Spring Boot, to build backend services.
        <br />
        <br />
        To support that I also developed frontend user interfaces using different
        frameworks, but most of the time I have used Angular + Typescript as main
        frontend technologies. Since then I'm trying to improve my knowledge learning
        new techs like Astro, JS in order to get a solid background in this area.
        <br />
        <br />
