        and getting helped and who is eager to continue growing and learning in the
        field of web development.
        <br />
        <br />
        Aside from developing, some other activities that I love to do are playing
        tennis, basketball and of course spend time with family.
        <br />
        <br />
        If you have any doubt don't hesitate to ask me via email using the button located
        at the top of the card. I'm excited to answer!
      </p>
    </div>
